  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1968",
  "title": "SearchBox doesn't have icons in Safari",
  "body": "**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\n\r\nIn Safari the icons of the search box don't show up\r\n\r\nVisible in for example: https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/react/storybook/?selectedKind=SearchBox&selectedStory=default&full=0&down=1&left=1&panelRight=1&downPanel=kadirahq%2Fstorybook-addon-knobs\r\n\r\n<img width=\"318\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-02-10 at 17 49 01\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6270048/22835513/58f36332-efb9-11e6-8510-4646fd1ef4f1.png\">\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\n\r\nThe search box has buttons with icons like in Chrome\r\n\r\n<img width=\"321\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-02-10 at 17 49 21\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6270048/22835506/52829d1a-efb9-11e6-9b8a-3cae023471c8.png\">\r\n\r\n**Bug: What browsers are impacted? Which versions?**\r\n\r\nAll current Safari versions can't display svg inside a `<button>`, mve:\r\n\r\nhttp://codepen.io/anon/pen/mRQMzW\r\n\r\n**What project are you opening an issue for?**\r\n- react-instantsearch\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\n\r\n3.1.0",
